subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Justine Henin won her ninth title of the season, beating 19-year-old Tatiana Golovin, 6-4, 6-4, at the Zurich Open. The top-ranked Henin won the final five games en route to her 20th consecutive victory in 13 tournaments this season.
